<!-- 3. 무료 학습 자료 -->
<section id="free-study" class="py-16 px-4 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="exam-heading-md mb-3">지금 바로 무료로 공부하세요</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500">교재 2~4권의 계약 실무 영역(수의계약·경쟁입찰·계약체결·이행관리)을 집중 커버합니다</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- 법령 가이드 -->
      <a href="https://silmu.kr/topics" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-all" style="box-shadow:0px 4px 24px rgba(25,28,29,0.05)">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 transition-colors" style="background:#f3f4f5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl transition-colors" style="color:#002b57">menu_book</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-xl mb-2">법령 가이드</h3>
        <div class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-2" style="color:#002b57;font-family:'Manrope',sans-serif">68개</div>
        <p class="text-slate-500">수의계약·경쟁입찰·보증금·이행관리 등<br>계약 전 과정 법령 조문 + 실무 해설</p>
        <div class="mt-5 font-semibold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all" style="color:#002b57">
          학습하기 <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">arrow_forward</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- 감사사례 -->
      <a href="https://silmu.kr/audit-cases" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-red-100 hover:border-red-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-red-500 transition-colors">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-red-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors text-3xl">gavel</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-xl mb-2">감사사례</h3>
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">100건</div>
        <p class="text-slate-500">실제 감사원·자치단체 감사 적발 사례로<br>배우는 위반 유형 + 처벌 규정</p>
        <div class="mt-5 text-red-600 font-semibold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all">
          사례 보기 <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">arrow_forward</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- 추천 학습 주제 -->
    <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl p-6 text-white" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#002b57,#174174)">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">tips_and_updates</span>
        시험 고출제 예상 주제 TOP 6
      </h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
        <% [
          ["수의계약 사유", "private-contract"],
          ["입찰참가자격", "bid-qualification"],
          ["계약보증금", "contract-guarantee-deposit"],
          ["지체상금", "late-penalty"],
          ["낙찰하한율", "lowest-bid-rate"],
          ["검수·검사 절차", "inspection"]
        ].each do |title, slug| %>
          <a href="https://silmu.kr/topics/<%= slug %>" class="bg-white/20 hover:bg-white/30 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-yellow-300 text-base">arrow_forward_ios</span>
            <%= title %>
          </a>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
